    },
    {
      "height": 122,
      "id": "08c088cccb4fe5df",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Vary the under-the-hood variables. Have weird doors, weird weights, weird implementations of rewire.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": -11175,
      "y": -8968
    },
    {
      "height": 278,
      "id": "e5ad857c88cf8a5d",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- Invert solution requirements (the solution becomes the obstacle, and vice versa)\n- misdirect with red herrings\n- same puzzle, different emphasis\n\nask \"how can this mechanic betray the player's first guess?\"",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 670,
      "x": -11785,
      "y": -9187
    },
    {
      "height": 82,
      "id": "3da759fab97dc361",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Take a previous concept and \"flip it on its head\"",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 393,
      "x": -11912,
      "y": -9280
    },
    {
      "height": 153,
      "id": "826b94cdac67d851",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Invert the on/off input of receiver devices, invert on/off output of output devices",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": -11175,
      "y": -9157
    },
