      },
      "text": "sewer-5\n- [x] four walls\n- [x] wall colors\n- [x] wall materials\n- [x] bridge\n\t- [x] railing\n\t- [x] rivets\n\t- [x] white seam\n- [x] multicolor chip plastic glass platforms\n- [x] stairs\n- [x] drainage gutter grate\n- [x] lore computers in corner? or recall?\n- [x] loot transport pipes for decoration\n\t- [x] copy from other\n\t- [x] bend elbow\n\t- [x] bend path\n\t- [x] make 2\n- [x] frog behind wall indentation for fun? (doesn't make noise)\n- [x] wires",
