    {
      "height": 780,
      "id": "43e165c2b4276a69",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### Lore (after NPCs & bosses)\nSewer 2\n- pipe system\n\t- why (transport batteries, metal balls placeholder for testing)\n\t- how (drilling and fitting)\n- nephew Raymond finally accepted on team\n- post-peace-award wishlist\n- retirement plan after working under [[Science Nerd]]\n\nToni wants a stable and easy job, which is why he gave up on being a pilot. He is a technician, an engineer.\n\nSewer 4\n- chandroid battery\n\t- Not Rosie's. It's an older model battery. It takes a lot of power to run a transport system, so a Chandroid battery is ideal.",
