      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 364,
      "x": 2740,
      "y": -1425
    },
    {
      "height": 160,
      "id": "3437701330bcd098",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Chemistry affordances should probably to to the [[Science Nerd]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 420,
      "x": 7560,
      "y": -4100
    },
    {
      "height": 200,
      "id": "15b4674e3fdc7fe2",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "I need to model affordances based on what the space is *actually* used for in the story.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 7510,
      "y": -4005
    },
    {
      "height": 330,
      "id": "d2764a1e431de52b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Science Nerd is also mystic. Maybe mystic affordances?\n\nThemes of the mountain should be mostly religious, but a little bit science.\n\nAdorn all science in the imagery of the death cult",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 340,
      "x": 7960,
      "y": -4070
    },
    {
      "height": 240,
      "id": "cd2840f1841dc6f2",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Dark blues, intimidating statuettes,\nlit by flames",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 8260,
      "y": -3905
    },
