      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Reminiscent of dark crateria",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 320,
      "x": 8620,
      "y": -3647
    },
    {
      "height": 780,
      "id": "4a1c1d824bede27e",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## Affordance Graph\n\n|          | City | Highway | Sewer | Suburbs | Beach | Discotech | Satellite | Mountains |\n| -------- | :--: | :-----: | :---: | :-----: | :---: | :-------: | :-------: | :-------: |\n| Rewire   |  ✔   |         |       |         |       |           |           |           |\n| Fall     |  ✔   |    ✔    |       |         |       |           |           |           |\n| Bounce   |  ✔   |         |   ✔   |         |       |           |           |           |\n| Swim     |  ❗   |         |   ✔   |         |       |           |           |           |\n| Lift     |      |         |       |    ✔    |       |           |           |           |\n| Push     |      |         |       |         |   ✔   |     ✔     |     ❗     |           |\n| Submerge |      |         |       |         |       |     ❗     |     ✔     |           |\n| Peek     |      |         |       |    ❗    |       |           |     ✔     |           |\n| Pull     |  ❗   |         |       |         |   ❗   |           |           |     ❗     |\n| Jump     |  ✔   |    ✔    |       |         |       |           |           |     ❗     |\n\nAffordances follow a rough line for progression. \nCells below the line are optional late-game content. \nCells above the line are \"victory laps\" for particularly fun mechanics.\nThe line mustn't be obscured by too much late-game content or else player will be confused. (mistake made by Blasphemous DLC)\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1320,
      "x": 7120,
      "y": -4920
    },
    {
      "height": 640,
      "id": "5ccdb1772377bdfb",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- Metroid Prime Trilogy\n- The Talos Principle\n- Hollow Knight\n- Manifold Garden\n- Antichamber\n- Animal Well\n- Scorn\n- Blasphemous\n- Half-Life 2\n- Minecraft\n---\n- Portal\n- The Witness\n- Hyper Light Drifter",
