    {
      "height": 1040,
      "id": "9826e3ce83023dec",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] replace minecraft model for pitstop interior\n\t- [x] explore best surface layout\n\t- [x] locker rooms roof\n\t- [x] locker rooms windows\n\t- [x] locker room girls\n\t- [x] locker room guys\n\t- [x] window room wall\n\t- [x] lobby desk\n\t- [x] lobby window\n\t- [x] window room window\n\t- [x] stairs enclosure\n\t- [x] pool roof\n\t- [x] tube enclosure\n\t- [x] floaties pedestal\n\t- [x] tube to pool\n\t- [x] tube half\n\t- [x] battery table\n\t- [x] pool water\n\t- [x] light windows in pool\n\t- [x] fix leaks\n- [x] couch\n- [x] pool chair\n- [x] tube base on roof\n- [x] interior pillars\n- [x] wall colors\n- [x] baked lighting\n- [x] curved pool with edge\n- [x] beautify doors",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 420,
      "x": 11140,
      "y": -6480
    },
    {
      "height": 120,
      "id": "17bfa7bb652f9af7",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Remember, only do the bare minimum to \"finish\"",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 10740,
      "y": -5560
    },
    {
      "height": 860,
      "id": "031e8b3ee75d959a",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] rotate tower bottom\n\t- [x] disconnect bottoms inside and outside\n\t- [x] parent appropriate pieces to bottom\n\t- [x] rotate\n- [x] break glass + remove fabric + remove rewire target\n- [x] round out platforms\n- [x] car enclosure shape, SIMPLE (ring around car + glass dome, maybe a central lip to imply sealed hemispheres)\n- [x] define building, SIMPLE (bevel corners, add roof extension, duplicate roof down for middle trim)\n- [x] fix bridges\n- [x] fix wires\n- [x] bg props\n\t- [x] mountains\n\t- [x] airport\n\t- [x] previous level\n\t- [x] next level\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 400,
      "x": 10300,
      "y": -6300
    },
    {
      "height": 760,
      "id": "7ba4c046f4d1d034",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] BUG: fog disappears after falling off (check dive script)\n- [x] bushes need colliders\n- [x] undersides\n- [x] round out bottoms of cliffs\n- [x] highway pitstop replace minecraft with probuilder\n\t- [x] platforms\n\t- [x] pitstop platform + building\n\t- [x] billboard\n\t- [x] COPY: tram destinations\n\t- [x] COPY: tower\n\t- [x] COPY: roof\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 440,
      "x": 9800,
      "y": -6200
    },
    {
      "height": 1080,
      "id": "69ec941883a1a618",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] materials\n\t- [x] walls\n\t- [x] floors\n\t\t- [x] divide up floor in lobby\n\t- [x] props\n\t- [x] ceilings\n- [x] floaties pedestal\n- [x] pad wire\n- [x] window sills\n- [x] exterior window curved outlines\n- [x] front desk\n- [x] pool atmospheric particles\n- [x] magazines on coffee table near entrance\n- [x] white seam UV on locker room doors\n- [x] power fork / lightmap switcher\n\t- [x] dark room looks good\n\t\t- [x] ambient lights\n\t\t- [x] light sources materials\n\n- [x] changing benches",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 480,
      "x": 11640,
      "y": -6520
    },
    {
      "height": 520,
      "id": "94e5fe02ddb1c83b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] make sci-fi nerd (box)\n- [x] make boss teleport to specific location\n- [x] spread locations around\n- [x] make noise when looked at (test without teleporter)\n- [x] stop, then teleport when looked at\n- [x] add companion interactible disabled by default\n- [x] special sneaking state after a set time when tech nerd is behind player (angle comparison)\n- [x] companion interactible is enabled, tablet is allowed\n- [x] when interacted, reduce boss health, turn off state, resume teleporting\n- [x] boss dies after 3 hits\n- [x] connect start and end",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 600,
      "x": 4480,
      "y": -5022
    },
    {
      "height": 660,
      "id": "0535e33b182ec36b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Tone Established (not dailies)\n- [x] apartment\n- [x] city\n- [x] sewer\n- [x] highway\n- [x] suburbs\n- [x] beach\n- [ ] club\n- [ ] satellite\n- [ ] mountains\n- [ ] codec\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 360,
      "x": 7780,
      "y": -6200
    },
    {
      "height": 480,
      "id": "3b10b5c1dfdc153d",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] detail blockage\n- [x] detail billboard \"REST STOP\"\n- [x] move billboard to building\n- [x] add entrance for secret\n- [x] add parking lot texture\n- [x] add wall textures and windows to building\n- [x] detail power emitter thingy\n- [x] detail entrances\n- [x] floor deco",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 360,
      "x": 10740,
      "y": -6200
    },
    {
      "height": 480,
      "id": "00cdd82a234f5f21",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Final room checklist:\n- [x] tram audio\n- [x] tram track\n- [x] bg ground textures\n- [x] bg fences\n- [x] bg building texture\n- [x] connection point between tower and roof\n- [x] roof UV finished\n- [x] roof prefab looped\n- [x] mountains north\n- [x] \"airport\" bg object\n- [x] \"pitstop\" bg object",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 480,
      "x": 9300,
      "y": -6200
    },
    {
      "height": 760,
      "id": "bffb2389c43ef300",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Changes to introduction\n\nPlayer starts in bedroom, having woken up after Chandroid.\nWalks over to her on balcony, speaks to her. \"Are you ready to go? I hope I'm right about this.\"\nScans on the laptop fill in details on the inciting event.\nCommands tutorial pops up immediately.\nFront door is never locked. \nLexie when spoken to in absence of Chandroid, \"Hey, `<playername>`. Good morning. Is `<companionname>` around?\"\n\nIn presence of Chandroid, \"Hey, you two. Where you going?\"\nChandroid says, with nervous look, \"We're about to go out looking. `<playername>` here stayed up all day and night tracking down our first lead.\"\n\n\"O-Okay. Be safe. And be back before too long, yeah? We'll have another game night, just the four of us. I remember how much you... used to enjoy those.\"\n\n**These changes remove exposition and humor in favor of player freedom and emotional gravity.**\nThe world can speak louder when the narrative is left a mystery.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1160,
      "x": 6540,
      "y": -6440
    },
    {
      "height": 420,
      "id": "b871e6453bbf6ed8",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Boss Themes\n- [ ] [[DnD Nerd]]\n- [ ] [[Tech Nerd]]\n- [ ] [[Fangirl Nerd]]\n- [ ] [[Octopus]]\n- [ ] [[Music Nerd]]\n- [ ] [[Sci-Fi Nerd]]\n- [ ] [[Science Nerd]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 8180,
      "y": -6200
    },
    {
      "height": 340,
      "id": "c0d58f0f9732b367",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Grab electric charge, short out \"lock\" on external gain knob, crank music nerd's gain 3 times\nobstacle?",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 320,
      "x": 3960,
      "y": -4520
    },
    {
      "height": 260,
      "id": "f20702c9e626b6de",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "use [[Breathing Device]] as tool to defeat boss\n\n\nboss entirely fought underwater!!!!",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 480,
      "x": 3920,
      "y": -4881
    },
    {
      "height": 140,
      "id": "241535bdcc55c2ac",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Each room has an artistic point. No room exists dependent on others for merit.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": 8620,
      "y": -6100
    },
    {
      "height": 630,
      "id": "c5d177d7566b1c6f",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Arachnae Boss",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 640,
      "x": 3460,
      "y": -6584
    },
    {
      "height": 540,
      "id": "701a11ddea05b9fa",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "\n\n- [x] electric zaps collectible\n- [x] short circuitable DAC\n- [x] water falls\n- [x] 3 sprocketable weak points\n- [x] boss loses health when weak points hit\n- [x] water rises\n- [x] player respawns as companion\n- [x] boss dies after 3\n- [x] bullet hell projectiles\n\t- [x] sine wave speed projectile\n\t- [x] projectile gets respawned over time\n- [x] difficulty increases slightly\n- [x] boss connected to start + end",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 440,
      "x": 3480,
      "y": -4200
    },
    {
      "height": 180,
      "id": "ed7f8a21266b9500",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Use chandroid's movement to crank gain",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": 3480,
      "y": -4440
    },
    {
      "height": 160,
      "id": "18c403c3f7089b38",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Goal to hurt [[Music Nerd]]'s ears by cranking the gain?",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 280,
      "x": 3400,
      "y": -4740
    },
    {
      "height": 238,
      "id": "2fda4c8c79e91644",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "How can we bring the joys of music production to this boss battle, using Chandroid mechanics?",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 3400,
      "y": -5000
    },
    {
      "height": 220,
      "id": "db9db5cf35d1abfd",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Each room in the game is a diorama.\nA work of art to which the following room is a sequel aesthetically.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 8620,
      "y": -6350
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "182b61d545baa203",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "progression gate based on apparel",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 8400,
      "y": -6460
    },
    {
      "height": 140,
      "id": "8da62afc2e92aa9a",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Music is melodic, yet ambient.\nMelody provides the heart, ambience provides the world.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 360,
      "x": 7820,
      "y": -6380
    },
    {
      "height": 630,
      "id": "5c5a60062d2e35e9",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Sci-Fi Nerd Boss\n- teleports around the room \n- jams signals to your tablet except when he's sneaking up on you\n- if you look at him while sneaking he'll teleport away\n- use tablet to command [[Chandroid]] to attack him\n- three times and it's done, the battery for his teleporter falls out of his cloak",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 680,
      "x": 2740,
      "y": -6584
    },
    {
      "height": 545,
      "id": "96e4d3a87ca5d968",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# What is a Chandroid boss?\n- I've said things like \"the ***real*** boss is the puzzle afterwards\"\n- tests of timing, speed, reaction, basic grasp of mechanics\n## Why?\n- serves narrative and spectacle purpose primarily\n\t- \"feel\" is more important than mechanical depth",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1420,
      "x": 1360,
      "y": -5879
    },
    {
      "height": 630,
      "id": "3d23b5714449de13",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Music Nerd Boss\n- DJ, rhythm, music, eq, compression, sidechain, arpeggio, citrus, serum, massive\n- each new attack is accompanied by a new sound design, it's actually a new bass he's been working on each time, which causes the speakers to shoot different types and colors of sounds\n- gauntlet of attacks to avoid, like bullet hell\n- once all rounds are survived, Music Nerd's sound system overloads and pops, letting its battery fall out, exposed",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 680,
      "x": 2020,
      "y": -6584
    },
    {
      "height": 1060,
      "id": "a4ba57d5060ba32b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "music verbs:\n- scratch\n- remix\n- boost\n- cut\n- spin\n- plug\n- synthesize\n- loop\n- rewind/reverse\n- drop\n- bang\n- stab\n- equalize\n- donk\n- glitch\n- tearout\n- compress\n- sidechain\n- pluck\n- filter\n- pan\n- delay\n- mute\n- monitor\n- feedback\n- limit",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 300,
      "x": 3080,
      "y": -5000
    },
    {
      "height": 280,
      "id": "c931d1a315cf2412",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "If the player obeys the music nerd, he just bids them farewell. An NPC tells the player he's actually looking for a great improv artist who can think outside the box. Maybe try mixing in some synth, and using all the drums.\nCorrect combo: Kick, synth, snare, hat",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 420,
      "x": 2570,
      "y": -4800
    },
    {
      "height": 160,
      "id": "d738fd503179d7f3",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "physical instruments, wires connected via repeaters to computer",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 340,
      "x": 2570,
      "y": -4980
    },
    {
      "height": 140,
      "id": "d5946c847188098f",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Music nerd captures chandroid for battery harvesting",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 310,
      "x": 2570,
      "y": -5140
    },
    {
      "height": 700,
      "id": "55198e4f1ff12a74",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Music nerd sequencing game\n\n- [ ] musical sprocketable buttons\n- [ ] wave 1: kick, kick, kick, kick\n- [ ] wave 1 obstacles, dodge kick waves coming from all directions\n- [ ] wave 2: kick, snare, kick, snare\n- [ ] wave 2: kick obstacle, snare obstacle\n- [ ] wave 3: kick, hat, snare, hat",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 500,
      "x": 2040,
      "y": -5060
    },
    {
      "height": 630,
      "id": "9b603f4f2a4ff400",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Octopus Boss\n- tests\n\t- platforming\n\t- bounce\n\t- sprocket push\n- obstacle course across [[Boardwalk]]\n- octopus is pulling down sections of the boardwalk and slamming tentacles down in front of the player\n- ends in cutscene where [[Chandroid]] catches a tentacle, before you black out and are taken to the [[Island]], where the Octopus hits itself on a rock and gets knocked unconscious, allowing you to enter its battery",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 620,
      "x": 1360,
      "y": -6584
    },
    {
      "height": 1062,
      "id": "f07e1f4eec158cc1",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "pushable objects:\n### Puzzle\n- variability based on force applied\n\t- speed of block\n\t\t- frictionless surface, small push = longer time\n\t- time until block comes back\n\t\n- push chunks of puzzles\n- timed paddle wheel\n- rotate room/round platform\n- pushable platform/lift/tram\n- sprocketing against any puzzle door 50 times will break it (for cheaters)\n### Gimmick\n- pully system\n- fence fall down\n- progressive paddle wheel (boost ball style)\n- domino props/enemies\n- push car\n- boat rotor\n- heavy shopping cart\n- fan belt\n- rattle/dislodge most decorations\n- block that slides to a halt\n- balloon game, force of air affects balloon's lift\n- inflating balloon, pushing fragile balloon to goal (full blast pops it)\n- launch water ball",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 740,
      "x": 660,
      "y": -3082
    },
    {
      "height": 640,
      "id": "35986926c3f88c67",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "No reason to ever vary the pressure applied by the sprocket gun. Even if it's possible to shoot weaker, there is never an advantage to doing so. Inverting the requirements doesn't solve the problem, either. There is never any reason to go \"middle of the road.\"\nYou need a qualitative difference for different force levels, not quantitative. And there must be a naturally occurring need to select different force levels.\n\nIn that sense, the sprocket gun is identical to a punch or kick.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": 1460,
      "y": -2900
    },
    {
      "height": 700,
      "id": "07ce48fcac577bf6",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "octopus boss\n\n- [x] make projectile (arc object)\n- [x] make projectile sprocketable\n- [x] make target\n- [x] make octopus throw by himself on a timer\n- [x] throw 2 urchins, one sprocketable ball\n- [x] make boss die after 3 hits\n- [x] variability of speed, fake-out throws\n- [x] create button upon boss death",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 540,
      "x": 1240,
      "y": -5060
    },
    {
      "file": "Pasted image 20251218111205.png",
      "height": 750,
      "id": "271c35e786bca72f",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 1102,
      "x": 520,
      "y": -7920
    },
    {
      "file": "Pasted image 20251219160455.png",
