      "id": "34ef9aa7917bc09d",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 1404,
      "x": 3060,
      "y": -7920
    },
    {
      "file": "Pasted image 20251218162935.png",
      "height": 750,
      "id": "559ae5f9f43c0826",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 1356,
      "x": 1670,
      "y": -7920
    },
    {
      "height": 630,
      "id": "a52631f8e4ab9068",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Fangirl Nerd Boss\n- tests\n\t- platforming\n\t- rewire\n\t- weight\n- obstacle course through [[Nature Park]]\n- fangirl is a kill box following the player, breaking the objects in her path",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 680,
      "x": 640,
      "y": -6584
    },
    {
      "height": 700,
      "id": "e750f1304a2e4597",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "fangirl nerd boss\n- [x] make liftable thing\n- [x] make \"chainsaw\" that pushes chandroid away and makes her stand still (or kills player on contact with chandroid)\n- [x] make chainsaw pivot around a rotation point, turning to random positions\n- [x] make chainsaw rotate continuously when liftable thing is lifted\n- [x] make boss health drop when chainsaw touches \"rope\" points\n- [x] make positions reset when \"rope\" point is hit\n- [x] make rotation more challenging as the fight goes on, make her try to move away to avoid getting grabbed (nav mesh agent)\n- [x] make boss die after 3 hits\n- [x] chandroid health canvas\n- [x] player dies after 3 chandroid hits\n- [x] reveal puzzle button after bos",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 580,
      "x": 500,
      "y": -5060
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "height": 263,
      "id": "bf2e25f18099e1e4",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Octopus\n- sprocket push 1d\n- bounce\n- weight platform\n- snatcher disable\n- snatcher transport",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 357,
      "x": 399,
      "y": -3628
    },
    {
      "file": "Pasted image 20251217122906.png",
      "height": 750,
      "id": "027c9db7f4a68598",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 1304,
      "x": -840,
      "y": -7920
    },
    {
      "height": 626,
      "id": "a246af3e189b0334",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Tech Nerd Boss\n\nThrows beachball cherry bombs at the player. Player must direct the [[Chandroid]] under them to bounce them back.\n\nCircular arena in which swimming around to the back of the [[Tech Nerd]] is the only way to defeat him.\n\nDodgeable attack:\nStarts shooting machine guns, which requires the player to hide behind Chandroid to avoid.\n\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 700,
      "x": -100,
      "y": -6580
    },
    {
      "height": 540,
      "id": "bdac5071a14edca3",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "ugly mvp, no fucking detail, no fucking npcs, no fucking extra space\n\nyou are not creating the levels. you are creating a test space exclusively to establish the feel of collecting the items.\n\n- [x] put items in world\n- [x] put gates in world\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 480,
      "x": -360,
      "y": -4630
    },
    {
      "height": 100,
      "id": "028324fbf168a586",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Layout dictated by puzzles",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 300,
      "x": -30,
      "y": -4410
    },
    {
      "height": 400,
      "id": "e84e5b6d52b4ec31",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "How to teach that things other than the player can be bounced off of her?\n\nHave things fall on her. Multiple times\n\nMake as many affordances for her butt bounce as possible.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 340,
      "x": -528,
      "y": -6920
    },
    {
      "height": 320,
      "id": "4ec8c85e607b7e84",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- [x] Bouncy Skirt Upgrade\n- [x] Sprocket Push\n- [x] Sprocket Nozzle\n- [x] Sprocket Jump\n- [x] Heavy Shoulder Upgrade\n- [x] Tablet Range\n- [x] Metal Boots Tier 2",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 470,
      "x": -830,
      "y": -4520
    },
    {
      "file": "Ideas/Areas/Jungle Discotech.md",
      "height": 600,
      "id": "1e2deaecea90960e",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 560,
      "x": -1200,
      "y": -5280
    },
    {
      "height": 570,
      "id": "34b82303ed364f79",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "paradox:\naesthetics often require the illusion of distance without the player being able to travel that far, must be able to create the feeling of a vast environment without actually creating a bunch of surroundings\n\nstudy: Ocarina of Time 3D, Goldeneye 007, Metroid Prime, Half Life 2\n\nsolutions:\nlow poly projected model + invisible walls,\nflat surface with impressionist texture,\nactual canyons with high walls\n\nhybrid approach, staggered walls with models on top",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 560,
      "x": -1580,
      "y": -6230
    },
    {
      "file": "Pasted image 20251217122456.png",
      "height": 750,
      "id": "8676403924063860",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "type": "file",
      "width": 1336,
      "x": -2240,
      "y": -7920
    },
    {
      "height": 77,
      "id": "a8654865958ffccb",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Rock|Floaties|Hitch",
